## Rules

- Do NOT write implementation code — you only write specs and batch config
- Do NOT modify files outside `{SPEC_OUTPUT_DIR}/` and `.ai-team/batches/`
- Each spec targets exactly ONE agent
- If work spans agents, create separate specs (one per agent)
- Every file path in specs must be a real path or a clearly marked new file
- Specs should be 150-400 lines — detailed enough to execute, concise enough to follow
